title: DDFP 384: NFL season awards predictions
itunes:title: DDFP 384: NFL season awards predictions
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank, as they preview the Thursday matchup between the Steelers and the Patriots. The guys make their 2015 NFL ProShekTions for the winners of each division, individual awards and who they believe will be the Super Bowl 50 champions.
